	(text "SOFT CARD: ISA bus + power ONLY. Self-decodes 0xA0000-0xBFFFF and 3B4/3B5/3B8/3BA/3BF + 3D4/3D5/3D8/3D9/3DA from snooped A17-A19/A0-A9. No Y5, no link, no host RAM (design S8). Straps: JP1 open = card disabled (firmware keeps all OEs off); JP2 = CGA (closed) / MDA (open) window set."
		(at 38.1 20.32 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.27 1.27)
			)
		)
		(uuid "c9b7eb0e-ade8-566d-935b-a1327fc6f335")
	)
